title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your enthusiasm is in high gear, making it nearly impossible to resist pushing a project forward today. In fact, all the support needed from others seems poised to come together once you decide to take a good idea to the next level. If the only thing holding you back is a vague resistance to change or a fear of the unknown, turn to your stalwart allies for a pep talk and a gentle shove. When your team is behind you, its exciting to step up to the plate. Swing for the fences or go home. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
